{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8e6faa83eb","title":"关于绝食静坐的问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bbdd69d8ec","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":29,"articleId":"8e6faa83eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fe2b63177f","type":"title","text":"关于绝食静坐的问题","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"8c249882be","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义制度下，无产阶级专政条件下，绝食静坐可以作为一种斗争手段。因为无产阶级内部有一小操敌人，有官主义。他无非要让你答应几个条件。所以绝食静坐，允许，但不能提倡，一般不赞成。绝食可以开水放糖、放盐、打葡萄糖，可以轮班。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"}],"page":{"id":"1c81455c37","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8e6faa83eb","start":510,"end":510}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3c7229b21a","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义制度下，无产阶级专政条件下，绝食静坐可以做为一种斗争手段。因为无产阶级内部有一小撮敌人，有官僚主义。他无非要让你答应几个条件。所以绝食静坐，允许。但不能提倡，一般不赞成。绝食可以开水放糖、放盐、打葡萄糖，可以轮班。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"bf817a23c8","type":"title","text":"关于绝食静坐的问题","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"}],"page":{"id":"5376b72a13","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"8e6faa83eb","start":610,"end":610}}}},"__N_SSG":true}